Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:03.27,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A shining step toward a glorious future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.19,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Of course, my heart's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.98,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}On an island that still believes in mermaids,\Na battle of deductions with Heiji Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:10.19,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}On the night of a festival, a case occurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.60,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:15.10,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
