Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:29.22,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrow of Dugong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.50,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Bikuni Shrine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:07.21,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimie Shimabukuro (27)\NSaori's Childhood Friend\NBikuni Shrine Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:46.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-Evil Arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:46.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,jugon
